pardus-idevice-mounter (0.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Add iOS device detection using libimobiledevice
  * Add device information display (name, model, iOS version, storage)
  * Add trust status checking
  * Implement device mounting and unmounting with ifuse
  * Add file manager integration
  * Add stale mount cleanup functionality
  * Setup Debian package structure

